subject: Davis Cup
Tennis
lead_paragraph: David Nalbandian and Guillermo Cañas gave Argentina a 2-1 lead against Sweden in their Davis Cup quarterfinal in Buenos Aires, beating Jonas Bjorkman and Robert Linstedt, 7-5, 6-4, 6-4.
